{"tid":592640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高潮眼爆紅】梁相宜被翻出兒時舊照 自小表演慾強","createTime":"2018-03-14T11:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T11:13:06.000Z","uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03b94ad63bdf1b0f1fa339409f48477c1716b812","tid":592640,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"在全國大人會議一次採訪上，一個反白眼，讓名不經傳的上海女記者突然爆紅，成為內地網民新歡。根據網民「肉搜」，這名「藐爆」同行的女記者，就是任職上海衞視第一財經台的梁相宜，洋名Leonie，畢業於中國傳媒大學。有認識她的網友指，梁看似強勢，「實際是個小綿羊的女記者。」<br />\n<br />\n有網友更翻出大量梁相宜的生活舊照，大多是飲飲食食、着靚衫行街時，由他人拍攝，亦有些她的個人童年照，身着舞衣學跳芭蕾舞，亦有張嘴唱歌，估計她自少已有甚強的表演慾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180313/large/1520927374_a757.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F1520927374_a757.jpg&h=53d4f9e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180313/large/1520927379_e768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F1520927379_e768.jpg&h=448cc471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180313/large/1520927380_a2ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F1520927380_a2ec.jpg&h=80ee508a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b061924e70c48dfb4425de510682f2c7bd08d16","tid":592640,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:13:06.000Z","msg":"雞味濃郁"}]}